  <data key="d2">**B人員**

B人員, also referred to as Engineer B in some contexts, is a critical role responsible for handling various aspects of maintenance. As per multiple descriptions, this individual is accountable for maintaining the records of C 客戶 and D 客戶 (customers) specifically, ensuring their needs are met. The engineer's responsibilities include not only handling maintenance tasks but also assisting with repair operations.

