  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Regulatory uncertainty refers to the unpredictability of government regulations and their impact on businesses.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulatory uncertainty is contributing to the decline in stock markets.&lt;SEP&gt;Regulatory uncertainty refers to the unclear or unpredictable regulatory environment that can impact businesses and markets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-d0d3b88d3601a1081c8354e0ef27952f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c0c6684aa00106f16e7869f519061642&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b6f1e5469f6278ea8a34bff96b293b69</data>
