<edge source="Noah Carter" target="100m Sprint Record">
  <data key="d7">14.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The 100m Sprint Record Held by Noah Carter

Noah Carter is recognized for setting a new 100m sprint record at the championship. This achievement was facilitated by his use of advanced carbon-fiber spikes, which contributed to an unprecedented performance. Carter's accomplishment underscores his exceptional speed and agility.

It is also documented that Carter broke the 100m sprint record, indicating a significant improvement over previous times. The exact timing of this record-breaking feat is not specified, but it is clear that Carter's performance was noteworthy.

