<edge source="C人員" target="B客戶">
  <data key="d7">11.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation between (B客戶, C人員) can be summarized as follows:

**Maintenance Responsibilities of C人員**

C人員, also referred to as personnel C or engineer C, play a crucial role in maintaining B客戶, which translates to customer B. Their primary responsibilities involve handling maintenance tasks for this specific customer.

According to various descriptions, C人員 are directly involved in the maintenance process for B客戶. They interact with Customer B to resolve issues and collaborate with other personnel, such as A人員, to ensure timely completion of these tasks.

Engineer C's involvement extends beyond mere interaction; they actively engage in maintenance activities related to customer B. This includes resolving maintenance requests, assisting in the upkeep of systems or equipment associated with B客戶, and performing tasks that guarantee the smooth operation of services catering to this particular customer.

A key aspect of C人員's role is their ability to work collaboratively with other personnel to ensure effective maintenance. This teamwork allows them to efficiently address the unique needs of B客戶, ensuring uninterrupted service delivery.

It is worth noting that while some descriptions mention A人員 assisting in maintenance tasks for B客戶, the primary responsibility of maintaining this customer falls under C人員's purview.

Through their dedicated efforts, C人員 ensure the ongoing satisfaction and trust of B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員is providing maintenance services to B客戶.&lt;SEP&gt;C人員負責對B客戶進行維護工作。&lt;SEP&gt;C人員handled B客戶's maintenance.</data>
