<edge source="C人員" target="E客戶維護紀錄">
  <data key="d7">8.0</data>
  <data key="d8">(C人員, E客戶維護紀錄)

C人員 is a crucial entity responsible for the upkeep and maintenance of the E客戶維護紀錄 system. Their primary role involves updating the records with the latest information, ensuring that all data is accurate and up-to-date. Additionally, C人員 is tasked with maintaining the overall functionality of the E客戶 system, addressing any issues or discrepancies that may arise.

In specific instances, C人員 has recommended updates to the Splunk software, such as transitioning from version 2025 MA to DM20250088_(8/12), and expanding authorization quantities for E客戶. These recommendations demonstrate their proactive approach to maintaining efficient systems and ensuring customer satisfaction.

The E客戶維護紀錄 is a critical tool used by C人員 in their daily tasks. As the responsible engineer, they handle the maintenance of E客戶's records, taking care to ensure that all necessary information is documented accurately. This collaboration between C人員 and the E客戶 system is essential for smooth operation and efficient customer service.

It is worth noting that while some descriptions suggest overlapping responsibilities, it appears that multiple engineers may be involved in maintaining different aspects of the E客戶 system. However, C人員's role remains central to the upkeep and maintenance of this critical customer record-keeping system.</data>
